step_data.thought: Now I'm on the My Account page. Looking at the page, I can see a 'Recently Ordered' section at the bottom of the page, which shows items that the user has ordered recently. I can see the 'Uttermost Volterra Crackled Taupe-Gray Ceramic Table Lamp' listed as the first item in this section. To add this to the cart, I need to check the checkbox next to this item and then click the 'Add to Cart' button below the list. I'll first check the checkbox for the lamp.
